                                            <footer class="notes"><h2 data-aid="138545841" id="notetitle1">Notes</h2><ol class="decimal" data-type="marker" start="1"><li class="footnote" id="note1-"><span class="label">1. </span><p data-aid="138545844" id="note1_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/gal/3.html?verse=27-28#p27" href="/scriptures/nt/gal/3.27-28?lang=eng#p27">Galatians 3:27–28</a>; emphasis added.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note2-"><span class="label">2. </span><p data-aid="138545847" id="note2_p1">See<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.html?verse=37#p37" href="/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.37?lang=eng#p37"> Doctrine and Covenants 20:37</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note3-"><span class="label">3. </span><p data-aid="138545849" id="note3_p1">See<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.html?verse=19#p19" href="/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.19?lang=eng#p19"> Mosiah 3:19</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note4-"><span class="label">4. </span><p data-aid="138545851" id="note4_p1">See<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/mosiah/18.html?verse=8#p8" href="/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/18.8?lang=eng#p8"> Mosiah 18:8</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note5-"><span class="label">5. </span><p data-aid="138545852" id="note5_p1">See<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/1-cor/13.html" href="/scriptures/nt/1-cor/13?lang=eng"> 1 Corinthians 13</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note6-"><span class="label">6. </span><p data-aid="138545854" id="note6_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/moro/7.html?verse=47#p47" href="/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.47?lang=eng#p47">Moroni 7:47</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note7-"><span class="label">7. </span><p data-aid="138545855" id="note7_p1">See Russell M. Nelson, “<a class="cross-ref" data-old-href="../../../..