p12" href="/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/7.12?lang=eng#p12"> 1 Nephi 7:12</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note13-"><span class="label">13. </span><p data-aid="138545865" id="note13_p1">See<a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/morm/8.html?verse=35#p35" href="/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.35?lang=eng#p35"> Mormon 8:35</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note14-"><span class="label">14. </span><p data-aid="138545866" id="note14_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/moro/6.html?verse=4-5#p4" href="/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.4-5?lang=eng#p4">Moroni 6:4–5</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note15-"><span class="label">15. </span><p data-aid="138545868" id="note15_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/nt/eph/2.html?verse=19#p19" href="/scriptures/nt/eph/2.19?lang=eng#p19">Ephesians 2:19</a>.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note16-"><span class="label">16. </span><p data-aid="138545869" id="note16_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.html?verse=20#p20" href="/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.20?lang=eng#p20">2 Nephi 31:20</a>; emphasis added.</p></li><li class="footnote" id="note17-"><span class="label">17. </span><p data-aid="138545871" id="note17_p1"><a class="scripture-ref" data-old-href="../../../../scriptures/bofm/moro/7.html?verse=48#p48" href="/scriptures/bofm/moro/7.48?lang=eng#p48">Moroni 7:48</a>.</p></li></ol></footer>
